<title type="html"><![CDATA[02/09 (Thu) Taiwan's traffic is a tourism problem / 7 things women need to know before joining the military (Host: May)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=699&amp;p=727#p727"><![CDATA[
02/09 (Thu) Taiwan's 'living hell' traffic is a tourism problem, say critics / 7 things women need to know before joining the military (Host: May)<br /><br />We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br /><span style="color: #400000"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="font-size: 200%; line-height: normal">摩斯漢堡明曜店</span></span></span><br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Agenda:<br /><br />7:00-7:20 pm : free talk<br />7:20-8:00 pm : session I, subgroup discussion <br />8:00-8:20 pm : break time<br />8:20-9:00 pm :  session 2, subgroup discussion<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session I<br />Taiwan's 'living hell' traffic is a tourism problem, say critics<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/travel/article/taiwan-traffic-war-tourism-intl-hnk/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/travel/article/ ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1. &quot;In Taiwan, the characteristic friendliness of Taiwanese people vanishes as soon as they get behind the steering wheel.&quot; Do you have any response to this sentence?<br />2. &quot;Taiwan is a living hell for pedestrians.&quot; Do you agree at this criticism? Are there any cities in the island that can be excluded from it?<br />3. Taiwan is the country with the highest locomotive density in the world. Why do Taiwan people like to ride motorcycles?<br />4. My father used to say that motorcycles are suicide cars. What are the dangers of riding a motorcycle?<br /><br /><br /><br />Session II<br />7 things women need to know before joining the military<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.businessinsider.com/7-things-women-need-to-know-before-joining-the-military-2020-4#1-sexual-assault-is-a-real-threat-1">https://www.businessinsider.com/7-thing ... l-threat-1</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. The period of compulsory military service is extended to 12 months. Do you think that every eligible boy would be happy to go for it? <br />    What would be the reasons if the ones are not happy to go?<br />2. Should women perform compulsory military service? <br />3. Are there any possible risks for those men who serve in the military? Do you have a story to share?<br />4. What can men learn through military service that will help them in the future? Do you have a story to share?<br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Fri Feb 03, 2023 2:51 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
